---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="Smart Advocacy · 智慧维权 | 诉讼经验才是最好的谈判筹码 | 何淼律师"
    description="很多人以为找了诉讼律师就一定要上法庭。事实恰恰相反——诉讼经验越丰富，庭外谈判越有力。何淼律师以15年出庭经验，帮客人在协商阶段争取最优结果。647-930-6688。"
  />
  <meta name="keywords" content="智慧维权,Smart Advocacy,何淼律师,庭外和解律师,诉讼律师谈判,settlement律师,Ontario家庭法谈判,华人家庭法律师,能谈则谈,family law settlement Ontario,Markham家庭法律师" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Smart Advocacy · 智慧维权 | 何淼律师" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="诉讼经验越丰富，庭外谈判越有力。何淼律师能谈则谈，该打则打，始终以客人的最大利益为准则。" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/smart-advocacy" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/smart-advocacy" />
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  [
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "LegalService",
      "@id": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/smart-advocacy#service",
      "name": "何淼律师 — Smart Advocacy · 智慧维权",
      "url": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/smart-advocacy",
      "telephone": "+1-647-930-6688",
      "email": "miao@miaohelaw.ca",
      "provider": {
        "@type": "Person",
        "name": "Miao He",
        "alternateName": ["何淼", "Mia He"],
        "jobTitle": "Family Law Lawyer",
        "knowsLanguage": ["zh-Hans", "en"],
        "hasCredential": [
          {"@type": "EducationalOccupationalCredential", "credentialCategory": "Law Society of Ontario — Member #83315K"},
          {"@type": "EducationalOccupationalCredential", "credentialCategory": "China Bar Association — Licensed"},
          {"@type": "EducationalOccupationalCredential", "credentialCategory": "Expert Witness — Chinese Family Law & Marriage Law"},
          {"@type": "EducationalOccupationalCredential", "credentialCategory": "Notary Public — Ontario"}
        ]
      },
      "serviceType": ["Negotiation", "Settlement", "Out-of-Court Resolution", "Family Law Litigation", "Smart Advocacy"],
      "areaServed": {"@type": "Province", "name": "Ontario"},
      "inLanguage": ["zh-Hans", "en"]
    },
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "itemListElement": [
        {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "首页", "item": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/"},
        {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "智慧维权", "item": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/smart-advocacy"}
      ]
    }
  ]
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">首页</a> › 智慧维权</p>
        <h1>Smart Advocacy · 智慧维权</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">诉讼经验越丰富，庭外谈判越有力</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content">
      <div class="content-inner">

        <h2>找了诉讼律师，是不是一定要上法庭？</h2>
        <p>很多客人第一次来见何淼律师，都会有这样的顾虑：何律师是诉讼型律师，找她是不是就意味着一定要打官司？</p>
        <p>事实恰恰相反。</p>
        <p>正因为何淼律师有丰富的出庭经验，她才能在谈判桌上帮你争取到更好的结果。一个真正懂诉讼的律师，清楚地知道你的案子哪一点上了法庭一定能赢，哪一点胜算不大。这种判断力，是普通谈判律师无法具备的。</p>

        <h2>诉讼经验，是最好的谈判筹码</h2>
        <p>当对方律师知道你背后站着一个随时可以出庭的诉讼律师，谈判桌上的底气就完全不同了。</p>
        <p>何淼律师在协商阶段，会把所有相关的 case law 摆在桌上，清楚告诉对方：如果这个案子走上法庭，你的风险在哪里。这不是恐吓，这是事实。正是这种基于诉讼经验的分析，让对方不得不认真权衡，最终做出让步。</p>
        <p>这也是何淼律师帮助许多客人在协商阶段达成 settlement 的原因——省去了漫长的诉讼周期，也大大节省了客人的经济成本。</p>

        <div class="case-box">
          <h3>真实案例</h3>
          <p>何淼律师曾接手一个案件，对方态度非常强硬，坚持要拿到一个不合理的金额，完全不肯让步。</p>
          <p>何律师接手后，系统整理了所有相关判例，逐条分析了对方在诉讼中面临的风险，清晰地呈现给对方及其律师。对方意识到，如果真的走上法庭，结果很可能对自己更不利。</p>
          <p>最终，对方让步了。客人不需要上法庭，就拿到了合理的结果。</p>
        </div>

        <h2>能谈则谈，该打则打</h2>
        <p>何淼律师的执业理念从来不是"能省则省"，而是"以客人的最大利益为准"。</p>
        <p>有些案件，对方表面上愿意协商，实际上是在用谈判拖延时间。这种情况下，继续谈只会让你处于被动。何淼律师会帮你识别这种策略，在必要时果断转入诉讼，不让对方利用协商拖住你。</p>
        <p>而对于真正可以协商解决的案件，一个为客人着想的律师，不应该把客人逼上法庭。只要有机会在庭外达成 settlement，何淼律师一定会尽力争取。</p>
        <p>但如果对方坚持要走诉讼这条路，何淼律师在法庭上同样可以全力为你代理，争取你应得的权利。</p>

        <h2>费用公开透明</h2>
        <p>何淼律师承诺，所有代理费用公开透明，不会收取任何不该收的钱。无论是协商阶段还是诉讼阶段，收费标准都会在开始前清楚说明。</p>

        <div class="cta-box">
          <p>想了解您的案件是否有机会在庭外解决？</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="cta-btn">预约咨询 → 647-930-6688</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: #2C2418;
    color: #FDFBF7;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #9A8060;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .breadcrumb a {
    color: #9A8060;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #D4A853;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #C8B99A;
  }
  .content {
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .content-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2C1810;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid #D4A853;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
  }
  p {
    color: #3A2C1A;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .case-box {
    background: #FDFBF7;
    border: 1px solid #EDE8DF;
    border-left: 4px solid #7A5A1A;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  .case-box h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #7A5A1A;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .cta-box {
    background: #2C2418;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .cta-box p {
    color: #C8B99A;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #D4A853;
    color: #1A1208;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover {
    background: #B8923F;
  }
</style>
